Confident that building strong networks is fundamental for the achievement of their institutional goals, SLO have a partnership with several associations dealing with the conservation of the Marsican brown bear and its habitat:&#xd;
Rewilding Apennines (www.rewildingeurope.com/areas/central-apennines/);&#xd;
Montagna Grande (http://www.montagnagrande.it/)&#xd;
Dalla Parte dell'Orso (http://www.dallapartedellorso.it/)&#xd;
Un Ponte con la Natura (http://www.pontenatura.org/).&#xd;
Furthermore, SLO cooperate with National Parks - such as the Abruzzo, Lazio and Molise NP, Majella NP, Gran Sasso and Laga Mountains NP, Sirente Velino Regional Park, Monte Genzana Alto Gizio Regional Reserve, Gole del Sagittario Regional Reserve, Zompo lo Schioppo Regional Reserve, the Isernia Province and the Asso-MAB organisation.
